372473.cms|title=Khalid Choudhary handed over Kalidas Samman|work=[[The Times of India]]|date=15 November 2002|accessdate=18 March 2009}}</ref> |Theatre |- |[[Ghulam Mohammed Sheikh]] |Plastic Arts |- |rowspan="4"|2003-04 |[[V.G. Jog]] |Classical Music |- |[[Chandralekha (dancer)|Chandralekha]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hinduonnet.com/2003/10/19/stories/2003101900711100.htm|title='Kalidas Samman' for Chandralekha|work=[[The Hindu]]|date=19 October 2003|accessdate=18 March 2009}}</ref> |Classical Dance |- |[[Gursharan Singh (playwright)]] |Theatre |- |[[Himmat Shah]] |Plastic Arts |- |rowspan="4"|2004-05 |[[Prabha Atre]] |Classical Music |- |[[Rajkumar Singhajit Singh]] |Classical Dance |- |[[Devendra Raj Ankur]] |Theatre |- |[[Nagji Patel]] |Plastic Arts |- |rowspan="4"|2005-06 |[[Zakir Hussain (musician)|Zakir Hussain]] |Classical Music |- |[[Kanak Rele]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/mag/2006/01/29/stories/2006012900240500.htm|title=Tryst with Mohiniyattam|author=Paul, G.S.|work=[[The Hindu]]|date=29 January 2006|accessdate=18 March 2009}}</ref> |Classical Dance |- |[[Ratan Thiyam]] |Theatre |- |[[Manjit Bawa]] |Plastic Arts |- |rowspan="4"|2006-07<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraphindia.com/1070511/asp/frontpage/story_7762930.asp|title=Sonal in full swing, VIPs walk - Dancer furious after Rajnath & Co leave midway|author=Kidwai, Rashid|publisher=[[The Telegraph (Kolkata)|The Telegraph]]|date=11 May 2007|accessdate=20 March 2009}}</ref> |[[Puttaraj Gavai]] |Classical Music |- |[[Sonal Mansingh]] |Classical Dance |- |[[Vimal Lath]] |Theatre |- |[[Shanti Dave]] |Plastic Arts |- |rowspan="4"|2007-08 |[[Balwantrai Bhatt|Pt. Balwantrai Bhatt 'Bhavrang']] |Classical Music |- |[[C.V. Chandrasekhar]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hindu.com/2008/08/22/stories/2008082255281300.htm|title=Chandrasekhar chosen for Kalidas Samman|work=[[The Hindu]]|date=22 August 2008|accessdate=18 March 2009}}</ref> |Classical Dance |- |[[Babasaheb Purandare]]<ref>{{cite