'''Sheri Anderson''' is an American television writer, producer, and author. She is the creative consultant on NBC's ''[[Days of our Lives]]'' alongside head writer [[Ron Carlivati]]. She is also the author of the fiction novel series, ''Salem's Secrets, Scandals and Lies'', based on ''Days of Our Lives''. Anderson was also creative consultant on ''[[The Spot]]''.<ref>Yant, Monica (July 23, 1996). "As the Cyber World Turns", ''[[St. Petersburg Times]]'', p. D1.</ref> 

